text.section:
The ordinances declaring the transfer of property between two (2) cities shall include, but not be limited to, the following:
A definition of the area to be transferred;
A statement of the financial considerations between the two (2) cities regarding the area and the terms of any financial agreements;
The resolution of any taxes or revenues from the area; and
A statement of the land use or zoning regulations which would be applicable to the area being transferred if planning and zoning is in effect pursuant to KRS Chapter 100 in either city.
